room_title: Escape room "The Bake Off" by Escape Games AZ in Phoenix
room_address: 12 N. Center Street, Suite 200 Mesa, AZ 85201
room_description: The baker you work for has made it into the final round of the national bake off and hopes to soon realize her dream of winning. However, someone has stolen her package of secret ingredient, so she’s sent you to find her spare container. Unfortunately, you don’t know what the ingredient is or where she’s hidden her backup. You have 60 minutes to find it before the bake off begins without her.
